<sections> 
  <clause id="_management_oversight_of_information_security" inline-header="false" obligation="normative"><title>Management oversight of information security</title><clause id="_general" inline-header="false" obligation="normative">   
  <title>General</title>   
  <requirement id="_e7709f4a-c09e-48e8-ab5d-6364c22e8416"><label>/ss/584/2015/general/632</label><subject>The Cloud Service Provider’s management and board of directors</subject><description><p id="_fcd12a9a-714c-4287-bc8a-d38ecd77b057">The Cloud Service Provider’s management and board of directors shall be responsible for the following requirements and audit procedures.</p>    
</description><specification exclude="true">     
  <p id="_7f7cb2f5-6380-455b-8119-7468b23bc024">be responsible for the following requirements and audit procedures</p>     
</specification></requirement>   
</clause>  
<clause id="_level_1_requirements_and_audit_procedures" inline-header="false" obligation="normative">   
  <title>Level 1 requirements and audit procedures</title>   
  <requirement id="_74b85d2e-22a4-434c-8d9f-974f28c7ead8"><label>/ss/584/2015/level/1</label><subject>The Cloud Service Provider’s management and board of directors</subject><specification exclude="false">     
  <ol id="_594dca19-9b85-4a7f-9816-6e94d518c6c5" type="arabic">      
  <li>      
    <p id="_65e82be8-78b5-4b1a-9d1f-e8063e6fe093">Managing information security risks related to people, process, technology and governance.</p>      
  </li>      
  <li>      
    <p id="_15b8c4ea-1c7c-4a33-9854-29054c8d48c2">Oversight of the effective implementation of the technology controls.</p>      
  </li>      
  <li>      
    <p id="_5d4bd3ca-f2e3-47ed-8a1c-624c87fc4d14">Oversight of risk management practices.</p>      
  </li>      
</ol>     
</specification>
<verification exclude="false">     
  <ol id="_e30fec9f-1677-42e8-a17e-b3325e500d4b" type="arabic">      
  <li>      
    <p id="_60724da8-e0b3-4114-80c4-3ee29dfb51cb">Determine that the responsibilities of management and board of directors in managing and overseeing information security risks are documented and communicated.</p>      
  </li>      
  <li>      
    <p id="_fdbe62aa-dc54-4c64-b9ca-457463a07077">Inspect documents such as meeting minutes and committee charter to identify the participants involved in the meeting or committee, their respective job functions and the reporting relationship.</p>      
  </li>      
  <li>      
    <p id="_8d345b50-8d66-4e49-81e0-bef8443d143c">Determine whether the management and board of directors meet regularly, at an appropriate and monitored frequency.</p>      
  </li>      
  <li>      
    <p id="_74e47a33-a680-466a-a0fc-54a8ef96cb09">Determine whether the information security function is headed by a Chief Information Security Officer (CISO) or similar function.</p>      
  </li>      
</ol>     
</verification></requirement>   
</clause>  
<clause id="_level_2_requirements_and_audit_procedures" inline-header="false" obligation="normative">   
  <title>Level 2 requirements and audit procedures</title>   
  <requirement id="_023520e4-0b2c-41e5-9745-d8fc5b89a489"><label>/ss/584/2015/level/2</label><inherit>/ss/584/2015/level/1</inherit><description><p id="_29b9c8df-097c-4c78-8345-4381fd1d4872">The requirements and audit procedures are the same as those in Level 1.</p>    
</description><verification exclude="false"/></requirement>   
</clause>  
<clause id="_level_3_requirements_and_audit_procedures" inline-header="false" obligation="normative"><title>Level 3 requirements and audit procedures</title><requirement id="_3e17b9a5-d5b2-470b-98d1-198c4495c225"><label>/ss/584/2015/level/3</label><inherit>/ss/584/2015/level/2</inherit><description><p id="_3dba502d-d64f-424a-bf36-eeefcb92f99e">The requirements are the same as those in Level 2.</p>    
</description><verification exclude="false"><p id="_9972b28c-395a-44ba-9411-9e977feb8238">The audit procedures are those in Level 1 and the following:</p>     
<ol id="_f0a32247-490f-4747-a85b-2799247590e9" type="arabic">      
  <li>      
    <p id="_f4d12fec-a6f1-42c3-98f7-38872a6d8615">Verify risks have been reviewed, understood, and addressed (i.e. including a cost benefit analysis) by management and the board.</p>      
  </li>      
</ol></verification></requirement>   
